prompts.frontCover:
Dynamic comic book style greeting card front, 2D flat illustration. The scene is an action-packed, exaggerated winter wonderland on a snowy mountain under a bright blue sky.

In the foreground, Lao Lao, transformed into a comic book character based on the photo, is expertly skiing downhill at high speed. She's in a dynamic pose, leaning into a turn, kicking up a spray of powdery snow. She's laughing with a wide, joyful expression. She is skillfully balancing a huge, overflowing boba milk tea in one hand, with large tapioca pearls frozen mid-air as they splash out of the top. She wears a stylish, brightly colored ski jacket and the same glasses from the photo.

Slightly behind her and to the side, Jordan, also transformed into a comic book character, is comically tumbling down the slope, skis and poles akimbo in a chaotic, tangled mess. He has a look of hilarious panic on his face, eyes wide, as a spilled boba tea flies through the air next to him.

The background features jagged, snow-covered mountain peaks and a few stylized pine trees. The entire scene has bold black outlines, vibrant, saturated colors (like electric blue, hot pink, and lime green), and uses Ben-Day dots for shading. A large, explosive sound effect bubble, like "WHUMPF!" or "KAPOW!", is near Jordan to emphasize his crash.

Centered in a clear area of the sky above the action, the text "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao!" is written in a beautiful, flowing, and easily readable handwritten cursive script.
